---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import SoundCloudEmbed from '../components/SoundCloudEmbed.astro';
import Gallery from '../components/Gallery.astro';

const galleryItems = [
  { src: '/images/artist-01.jpg' },
  { src: '/images/artist-02.jpg' },
  { src: '/images/artist-03.jpg' },
  { src: '/images/artist-04.jpg' },
  { src: '/images/artist-05.jpg' },
];
---

<Layout title="Artist/Band" description="Recording services for artists and bands at The Hilson Studio, Nashville.">
  <section class="page-hero container">
    <p class="lede">Find your sound</p>
    <h1>Artists/Bands</h1>
  </section>

  <section class="block container prose">
    <p>You've got a sound, a style, a song. As Bob Ross always said, "All you need...is a few tools, a little instruction, and a vision in your mind." The Hilson Studio is the place to put it all together into one package.</p>
    <p>Whether it's a gritty acoustic & vocal recording free from hum and hiss you might get in a bedroom, a full rock arrangement with big real drums and electric guitars, or a synth based pop sound with stacked harmonies, it can all be done here.</p>
    <p>We've got the right gear to get a ton of different sounds, and you may even find some new ones as you work up a single, EP, or full length record. In addition to the facility itself, we have relationships with other musicians if you need to bring in some outside players, for a live string ensemble, vocal harmonies, or those metal blast beats your drummer always struggles with. We won't tell anyone. We're very discreet.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="block container">
    <Gallery items={galleryItems} />
  </section>

  <section class="block container prose">
    <blockquote class="testimonial">
      <p>"I've had the opportunity to work with Sean on three projects now. The first time I walked in with a few ideas and some lyrics and left with an entire album that I was extremely proud of. With Sean, you get it all- a quality producer, a talented musician, and an easy to work with business partner."</p>
      <cite>— Jeremy Simms, Rock/Worship, Birmingham AL</cite>
    </blockquote>
    <blockquote class="testimonial">
      <p>"Sean's experience in the studio and expertise with production make the entire recording process both easy and enjoyable for the artist. Whether I just need vocals recorded or want a fully produced track, The Hilson Studio is a no-brainer choice to get the quality product I am looking for."</p>
      <cite>— Alxxa, Pop/Electro, Nashville TN</cite>
    </blockquote>
  </section>

  <section class="block container prose">
    <h2>Listen to some samples of full production projects</h2>
    <p>tracked and mixed here at the studio.</p>
    <SoundCloudEmbed url="https://api.soundcloud.com/playlists/192992378" title="Full Production" />
  </section>
</Layout>
